    <p class="mb-6 text-base01">I'm Lucas de Oliveira (<b>@lucasxciv</b> on most social media platforms), a software developer since 2013. Over the years, I've worked in various areas of software development, but I've primarily worked with backend tasks using PHP. Currently, I work as an independent software developer and consultant, based in Cruzeiro, SÃ£o Paulo, Brazil.</p>

