    <p class="mb-6 text-base01">As a software developer primarily working on web applications and APIs, I've often found myself working on other parts of the product as well. I've worked on frontend tasks using SPA frameworks, set up continuous integration pipelines with cloud tools, contributed to mobile and desktop apps, helped with cloud platform deployments, built automation tools, led development teams, etc.</p>

